</div>
<!-- SECTION "Sample Microconf Schedule" [476-808] -->
<h2><a name="takeaway" id="takeaway">Takeaway</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

Hopefully increased participation on shared solutions that every distro can benefit from.
</p>

</div>
